West German producer prices fell 0.3pct in February from January and were 4.2 pct below prices inFebruary last year, the Federal Statistics Office said.    In January, producer prices rose 0.2 pct from December, thefirst monthly rise since October 1985, but they were down 4.4pct from a year earlier.    The Statistics Office said light heating oil producerprices fell 22 pct in February from January while heavy heatingoil prices fell 24 pct. REUTER&#3;